fields.value: Replication Data for: Neonatal nasogastric tube feeding in a low-resource African setting – using ergonomics methods to explore quality and safety issues in task sharing.

dsDescriptionValue.value: Data describing the use of Ergonomics methods in eliciting quality and safety issues during task sharing in selected neonatal settings in Kenyan neonatal inpatient settings. This is part of the larger work carried out by the Health Services that Deliver for Newborns (HSD-N) project
